title: Tackling Insecurity with Vulnerability
description:
It doesn't matter how successful you are, how many likes you get on Instagram, or even how many friends you have. We all have insecurities... including Judah and Chelsea. We'll hear about the critical inner voice that fuels insecurities, how to be vulnerable and accept ourselves for who we are, and ultimately — how to turn insecurities into strength. All that and more on this week’s In Good Faith.
